{"tid":511891,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"你地係點食雪糕","createTime":"2017-12-28T02:23:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T16:24:21.000Z","uid":45190,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"c47101e892a4d6f478f7fde14f0ca93666cc246a","tid":511891,"uid":45190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T02:23:12.000Z","msg":"生平大概見過幾種食法<br />\n<br />\n1. lam<br />\n條舌頭由下而上lam雪糕，好處係可以細味慢慢品嚐，壞處係條舌頭會好攰。<br />\n<br />\n2. 咬<br />\n一口一口咬雪糕，好處係大大啖咬入口感受冰凍嘅刺激感，壞處係食兩啖就食完。<br />\n<br />\n3. 吸<br />\n像濕吻般和雪糕打車輪，用嘴唇沾滿雪糕，再大大力吸啜，將雪糕快速咁通過嘴唇直到喉嚨，好處係可以感受到法國激情般嘅浪漫同雪糕談一場轟烈嘅戀愛，壞處係食到成面都係。<br />\n<br />\n利 吸啜派<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8015447741b3e4cf0fa357294b95c31015a4928b","tid":511891,"uid":143686,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T02:53:40.000Z","msg":"你個吸既形容笑到我氣喘"},{"pid":"9e39358d053798d5f76bc0783df582a951343cdf","tid":511891,"uid":45190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8015447741b3e4cf0fa357294b95c31015a4928b","tid":511891,"uid":143686,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T02:53:40.000Z","msg":"你個吸既形容笑到我氣喘"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T03:02:17.000Z","msg":"咁到底你係點食雪糕？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b56baba0e2e7b72f47e12ece02bdf89e8725f7","tid":511891,"uid":45190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T03:03:22.000Z","msg":"連登係咪無人食雪糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f19677f30525183dc6223de2cfd407a33d99c39","tid":511891,"uid":147538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T03:03:41.000Z","msg":"奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0d18d4439582736b8116cca1ebc05fe4485497","tid":511891,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T03:04:34.000Z","msg":"Lam<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 