g src=\"http://img.ziines.com/600x338/ziines-user-upload/upload/2016/10/19/34856_20161019234531_5807951bedd71.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ziines.com%2F600x338%2Fziines-user-upload%2Fupload%2F2016%2F10%2F19%2F34856_20161019234531_5807951bedd71.gif&h=f7643675&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57924978855fe13de0aef288889715a0ae0ad8f3","tid":511891,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T12:27:44.000Z","msg":"插碌鳩入去啜"},{"pid":"0629c5a49d935bc38158c0c40f4d37ef16bd22ad","tid":511891,"uid":136502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T03:01:57.000Z","msg":"我係幾個之間<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n先由根部從下而上咁奶<br />\n然後係頂尖度用條俐打圈<br />\n再由上而下奶番落去根部<br />\n此時嘅雪糕開似溶 所以必須轉動雪糕 <br />\n而條俐貼住根部防止啲水滴落隻手度<br />\n然後當處理好時 而口腔適應咗個感覺之後<br />\n就會係頂尖位輕輕咬 唔係咬曬<br />\n因為第一 好易足法敏感牙齒<br />\n第二雪糕好快食完<br />\n所以輕咬時亦不忘舌頭快速打轉 去補償快感<br />\n最後 雪糕去到適當長度 便深喉頂撞 使其雪糕能夠高速溶解 滲入喉嚨之中<br />\n體驗出無比快感<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇人都係咁食？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7bffb229fe8cfe0f24ef34af5851ba57b3cd04c","tid":511891,"uid":56115,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T03:09:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://gifgifmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/crnac-jede-sladoled.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgifgifmagazine.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2Fcrnac-jede-sladoled.gif&h=5ad3da7a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}